"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:20:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾先要著鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544b2805376d089ccdd6fcb8ee0025c2cbdf5879","tid":86922,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:20:59.000Z","msg":"Kyrie3"},{"pid":"9ad85fa611a071daf20992ce04f210aeac6d2859","tid":86922,"uid":65613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39ad208e98c10768f77b3baa67a4cfd8328fac71","tid":86922,"uid":77384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一對賣900，一對賣千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就由lebron elite 13 轉過去kyrie 3<br />\ncurry3冇著過唔敢講<br />\nkyrie 3 鞋前半部好大好闊，好處我覺得好穩定lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 壞係前腳有好大空間，前腳冇包裹感<br />\n鞋邊孤型的確對轉向好順<br />\n難抓地整體好滿意，街場一定冇問題<br />\n中筒鞋，縛實鞋底好快會鬆，冇ankle保護感<br />\n重量合適，冇kobe咁誇，亦冇lebron咁重<br />\n重過kd少少咁<br />\n<br />\n總結，，，整番個魔術貼啦大佬</blockquote><br />\n上網睇kyrie話完全冇cushion <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚落地收皮"},{"pid":"4e8f7f7002fbd93e498aa87d1417c5fecd930a06","tid":86922,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:30:53.000Z","msg":"呢期nike買三件野有65折<br />\n<br />\nKobe XI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939734a0e6d6e60360334370b45569673d76ee9d","tid":86922,"uid":66126,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"玩玩具都要着鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb19951a25e7b0491477ea7aafb086096ce71a8","tid":86922,"uid":77384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢期nike買三件野有65折<br />\n<br />\nKobe XI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nKobe 個腳踭位好撚厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4e96fdc1d3192e421427fc486bdcec94467100","tid":86922,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"Kyrie 3: 無kyrie2包裹性咁好，因為無左條魔術貼。不嬲kyrie系列都係無cushioning 咁制，舒適性差九條街，但對於一d速度快、鐘意插花、變向既巴打會好鐘意，因為個底非常responsive，你一俾力，個地就直接反饋翻道力俾你，觸地感非常清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCurry 3: 包裹性幾好，under armor響鞋後踭既設計比Nike 同adidas好，著上腳你會覺得同對鞋融為一體，當然，你要買岩碼，Curry系列會比較偏細半碼，記得塊試清楚，唔好先入為主試著開果隻碼就算，大/細半碼都試下佢，試到岩為止。cushioning 都不過不失，著落去會覺得個底比較厚，比較難感覺到塊地，但尚算靈活。"},{"pid":"f15afb2a4007f34662d8bd31fe417f2d1fe97e8a","tid":86922,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"利申：有Kd9, kyrie2, curry2<br />\n<br />\n個人感覺：<br />\n<br />\n室內場 KD9&gt;curry2&gt;kyrie2<br />\n<br />\n室外場 Kyrie2&gt;curry2&gt;kd9"},{"pid":"aa6b6eed6745f16016efeea8f2cd14d6b29bc2a2","tid":86922,"uid":40075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一對賣900，一對賣千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就由lebron elite 13 轉過去kyrie 3<br />\ncurry3冇著過唔敢講<br />\nkyrie 3 鞋前半部好大好闊，好處我覺得好穩定lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 壞係前腳有好大空間，前腳冇包裹感<br />\n鞋邊孤型的確對轉向好順<br />\n難抓地整體好滿意，街場一定冇問題<br />\n中筒鞋，縛實鞋底好快會鬆，冇ankle保護感<br />\n重量合適，冇kobe咁誇，亦冇lebron咁重<br />\n重過kd少少咁<br />\n<br />\n總結，，，整番個魔術貼啦大佬</blockquote><br />\n上網睇kyrie話完全冇cushion <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚落地收皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nKyrie 3 cushion 遠差過 Kyrie 2<br />\n<br />\n(Kyrie 2 同 Kyrie 3 cushion設計差唔多一樣，但Kyrie 2 用左 鞋墊 ortholite, 所以cushion還可以接受，但係Kyrie 3冇左， 我本人覺得唔可以接受，前掌好似著白飯魚一樣）<br />\n<br />\n係就係起步快，但打一陣對腳已經好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n我打開PG都接受唔到<br />\n<br />\n有時jumpshoot 要前腳掌落地好唔掂"},{"pid":"50def2ffb986d3a0be15ff2d525df92c80192ef1","tid":86922,"uid":77384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申：有Kd9, kyrie2, curry2<br />\n<br />\n個人感覺：<br />\n<br />\n室內場 KD9&amp;gt;curry2&amp;gt;kyrie2<br />\n<br />\n室外場 Kyrie2&amp;gt;curry2&amp;gt;kd9</blockquote><br />\nChing 點睇KD9 <br />\n紅色定綠色好"},{"pid":"94e0bfcac9890957c6130fb0cda4a775ef0b4b6d","tid":86922,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申：有Kd9, kyrie2, curry2<br />\n<br />\n個人感覺：<br />\n<br />\n室內場 KD9&amp;amp;gt;curry2&amp;amp;gt;kyrie2<br />\n<br />\n室外場 Kyrie2&amp;amp;gt;curry2&amp;amp;gt;kd9</blockquote><br />\nChing 點睇KD9 <br />\n紅色定綠色好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKd9 非常貼腳，同埋好難著，仲窄過處女。但塞左隻腳入去就好舒服，全掌air好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  條鞋帶可有可無，因為佢個鞋面會緊迫住你隻腳，所以你隻腳踭會完全貼晒響鞋踭，變左腳指位（前掌）會鬆好多。不過Kd9打石屎地應該就唔襟著，因為個底唔係xdr，打室內場就好ok"},{"pid":"7174f6ff85ec7b19f4ae4a9c85652bec6744d972","tid":86922,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申：有Kd9, kyrie2, curry2<br />\n<br />\n個人感覺：<br />\n<br />\n室內場 KD9&amp;amp;gt;curry2&amp;amp;gt;kyrie2<br />\n<br />\n室外場 Kyrie2&amp;amp;gt;curry2&amp;amp;gt;kd9</blockquote><br />\nChing 點睇KD9 <br />\n紅色定綠色好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我買左灰色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3d4a22df6e1461e7ea8f4f3569b35f6b7b0923","tid":86922,"uid":36686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:33:07.000Z","msg":"買Hyperdunk 2016 Low好過啦<br />\n再唔係試下Crazylight Boost 2016"},{"pid":"4a0f7ea366a6f849d1a65f067391a34d26d4c8c5","tid":86922,"uid":5804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n利申 買左kyrie2，適應左又幾滿意"},{"pid":"5007509f68ad30503a0c610a0259d4808bf18f7b","tid":86922,"uid":36686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy